Privacy Policy
Your privacy is very important to us. Accordingly, we have developed this policy in order for you to understand how we collect, use, communicate and disclose and make use of personal information.
The following outlines our privacy policy:
• Before or during the process of gathering any data, we clarify the intended purposes for the information being collected. It's important to note that we do not collect any personal information.
• Personal data should be relevant to the purposes for which it is to be used, and, to the extent necessary for those purposes should be accurate, complete, and up-to-date.
• We will make readily available to customers information about our policies and practices relating to the management of personal information.
• Our app integrates the AppLovin SDK, which collects device identifiers (such as Advertising ID, Android ID, IMEI, BSSID, MAC address) for advertising purposes. These identifiers are utilized by AppLovin to deliver personalized advertisements, measure ad performance, and optimize ad targeting within the app. The collected device IDs may be shared with third-party advertisers or ad networks to facilitate targeted advertising. Users can manage ad personalization settings via their device settings and may choose to opt-out of targeted advertising.
• Our app incorporates the AppsFlyer SDK, primarily used for referral and invitation purposes. AppsFlyer's functionality enables the facilitation of user referrals and invitations, fostering engagement within the app. While maintaining user privacy, the SDK collects specific device information, including the User ID, to attribute referral sources. This collected data assists in inviting players and managing referral campaigns.
• Our app only stores user progress within the app, and does not collect or store any other personal information from your Apple or Facebook account. We do not share your progress data with any third parties, except as required by law.
• When you sign in using Apple or Facebook, we gain access to your public profile information, We utilize Apple or Facebook solely as a sign-in method, ensuring that no personal information is accessed or utilized for our app's functionalities.
• Account Deletion: Our app allows you to delete your account and all associated data at any time. When you request account deletion, All your progress and purchases will be deleted, deletion process may take up to 30 days. Please note that once your account is deleted, we cannot recover any of your data.
We are committed to conducting our business in accordance with these principles in order to ensure that the confidentiality of personal information is protected and maintained.
PRIVACY INFORMATION
NG SLOT collects personal information about you in order to provide you with the Service, process your registration and for purposes otherwise set out in our private policy.  The information you provide will be collected by us or on behalf of us and may be disclosed to third parties that help us deliver our services (including information technology suppliers, communication suppliers and our business partners) or as required by law. If you do not provide this information, we may not be able to provide the Service to you.
By providing your personal information to us, you consent to the collection, use, storage and disclosure of that information as described in the Private Policy and this collection notice.
When you complete the NG SLOT registration process, you create a NG SLOT account . Your Account may also include billing information you provide to third-party payment processors for the purchase of virtual items. You may not reveal, share or otherwise allow others to use your password or Account except as otherwise specifically authorized by NG SLOT. You are responsible for the confidentiality of your login and password and for the security of your computer system. NG SLOT is not responsible for the use of your password and Account or for all of the communication and activity on NG SLOT that results from use of your login name and password by you, by any person to whom you may have intentionally or by negligence disclosed your login and/or password in violation of this confidentiality provision, or by any other person who fraudulently used your login and password without your permission. If you believe that the confidentiality of your login and/or password may have been compromised, you must notify PAYMENT TEAM EMAIL  without any delay.
You acknowledge that personal information that you communicate publicly within the Service may be seen and used by others and may result in unsolicited communications. NG SLOT is not liable for any information that you choose to submit or communicate to other users on or through the Service, or for the actions of any other users of the Service. You represent and warrant that you have all necessary rights in and to any materials that you post within the Service, that such materials do not infringe any proprietary or other rights of third parties, that all such content is accurate and will not cause injury to any person or entity, and that you will indemnify NG SLOT  and its Affiliates, and their respective employees, contractors, agents, representatives, vendors, and content providers, for all claims resulting from your submitted and posted content. If any such materials incorporate the name, voice, likeness and/or image of any individual, you represent and warrant that you have the right to grant NG SLOT permission to use any such name, voice, likeness and/or image of such individual appearing in the materials you post throughout the world in perpetuity. Once you post or communicate any content or materials on or through the Service, you expressly grant NG SLOT the complete, worldwide, fully sublicensable and irrevocable right to quote, re-post, use, reproduce, modify, adapt, publish, translate, create derivative works from, display, distribute, transmit, and broadcast such content or materials, including without limitation the name you submit in connection with such content or materials, in any form, with or without attribution to you, and without any notice or compensation to you of any kind. We reserve the right to immediately remove any content that may be considered, in our sole discretion, in violation of the rights of any third party.
